# SvelteKit Rules

## Svelte 5 Runes
- `$state()` for reactive state
- `$derived()` for computed values
- `$effect()` for side effects
- `$props()` for component props

## File Routing
- Data: `+page.server.ts` (server-only) or `+page.ts` (universal)
- Mutations: form actions in `+page.server.ts`
- Auth: `+layout.server.ts`

## Never
- Writable stores for local state (use `$state()`)
- API routes for simple CRUD (use form actions)
